name: SYNAPZ
description: SYNAPZ is an AI-driven blockchain project that integrates a multi-node “swarm intelligence” architecture with real-world software utilities. The project is built around a 64-node distributed AI system designed to perform tasks such as workflow automation, data processing, research assistance, customer-management support, and operational tools for businesses. The SYNAPZ token functions as the access layer for these utilities, enabling users to interact with AI agents, dashboards, automation modules, and future ecosystem services. The project is operated by a registered UK company (SYNAPZ AI Ltd) and is positioned as an applied-AI platform with both digital and real-world use cases.
